                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4"><a href="page-blog-post-right-sidebar.html"><img src="img/news2.jpg" alt="Post Title"></a></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-8">
                            <div class="caption"><a href="page-blog-post-right-sidebar.html">New Career Oportunities</a></div>
